    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"623\" data-end=\"660\">Glorious Past — Legacy of Resolve</strong><br data-start=\"660\" data-end=\"663\" /><em data-start=\"663\" data-end=\"709\">Caern State (from Rite of the Glorious Past)</em></p><p data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"768\">The Caern is bound to remembered sacrifice and endurance.</p><p data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"989\"><strong data-start=\"770\" data-end=\"828\">Effect (Active while this state remains on the Caern):</strong><br data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"831\" />While within this Caern’s area, <strong data-start=\"863\" data-end=\"872\">Garou</strong> have advantage on saving throws made to resist being <strong data-start=\"926\" data-end=\"940\">frightened</strong> or overwhelmed by <strong data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"988\">supernatural fear effects</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1000\"><strong data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1000\">Notes</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1001\" data-end=\"1189\"><li data-start=\"1001\" data-end=\"1048\"><p data-start=\"1003\" data-end=\"1048\">Applies only <strong data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1048\">within the Caern’s influence</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1073\"><p data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1073\">Affects <strong data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1073\">Garou only</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1074\" data-end=\"1189\"><p data-start=\"1076\" data-end=\"1189\">This state remains until <strong data-start=\"1101\" data-end=\"1130\">Rite of the Glorious Past</strong> is performed again (replacing it) or the <strong data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1189\">Caern is lost</strong></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1316\"><strong data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1215\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"1215\" data-end=\"1218\" /><code data-start=\"1218\" data-end=\"1316\">[GAROU_CAERN_STATE] parent=glorious-past; effect=legacy-of-resolve; exclusiveGroup=glorious-past</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"2944\" data-end=\"2978\">Glorious Past — Storied Ground</strong><br data-start=\"2978\" data-end=\"2981\" /><em data-start=\"2981\" data-end=\"3027\">Caern State (from Rite of the Glorious Past)</em></p><p data-start=\"3029\" data-end=\"3096\">The Caern’s story is heavy enough to withstand a moment of neglect.</p><p data-start=\"3098\" data-end=\"3283\"><strong data-start=\"3098\" data-end=\"3156\">Effect (Active while this state remains on the Caern):</strong><br data-start=\"3156\" data-end=\"3159\" />Once before this Rite is performed again, the Caern may <strong data-start=\"3215\" data-end=\"3247\">ignore the Corruption gained</strong> from <strong data-start=\"3253\" data-end=\"3282\">one missed monthly upkeep</strong>.</p><ul data-start=\"3285\" data-end=\"3454\"><li data-start=\"3285\" data-end=\"3338\"><p data-start=\"3287\" data-end=\"3338\">This does not prevent Corruption from other causes.</p></li><li data-start=\"3339\" data-end=\"3454\"><p data-start=\"3341\" data-end=\"3454\">After it is used once, this state is considered <strong data-start=\"3389\" data-end=\"3398\">spent</strong> (but may remain as a “0 uses” reminder until replaced).</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"3456\" data-end=\"3615\"><strong data-start=\"3456\" data-end=\"3480\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"3480\" data-end=\"3483\" /><code data-start=\"3483\" data-end=\"3615\">[GAROU_CAERN_STATE] parent=glorious-past; effect=storied-ground; exclusiveGroup=glorious-past; charges=1; consumedBy=missed-upkeep</code></p>"
    },
